cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

This paper deals with visual recognition and image classification, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep neural networks (cs.LG) and unsupervised learning (cs.AI) for part-based image classification. Additionally, the proposed approach has potential applications in instance-based image retrieval (cs.IR) and indexing tasks (cs.MM).
